metadata.title: ‘$1 trillion squad’: AI images of Musk, Altman, Huang, Cook with other billionaires spark frenzy
metadata.description: The exaggerated realism, combined with the uncanny nature of the images created using Grok and Nano Banana, among other AI tools, blurred lines between fact and fiction, prompting many to initially wonder if the photos were genuine. Even after confirmations that they were AI-generated, the debate only amplified the meme storm.
